### DotnetApp — HTTP request collection (VS Code REST Client / Visual Studio / Rider)
#
# Usage:
#   - Start the API:  dotnet run --project src/DotnetApp
#   - Click "Send Request" above any request below.
#   - Switch @host between the values to target http / https / docker.
#
# Per-feature collections live in this same folder, e.g. http/auth.http

@host = http://localhost:8000
# @host = https://localhost:8080
# @host = http://localhost:8080      # docker compose (api service)

### Health check
GET {{host}}/
Accept: application/json
